\n無乜路燈個啲，什至可能要摸黑咁落番黎<br />\n如果幾個人又有電筒應該無咩問題嘅，毒遊嘅話最好唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n另外，可以去試下騎士餐廳，好靚之餘8,9點時每15-20分鐘有一個表演睇。知幾時去嘅最好book位。有興趣可以上佢個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjJAKk0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjJAKk0.jpg&h=2b250ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/03/195717_8620dfb143fce05d0c91f30601381677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F03%2F195717_8620dfb143fce05d0c91f30601381677.jpg&h=97817db1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/03/195718_8620dfb143fce05d0c91f30601381677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F03%2F195718_8620dfb143fce05d0c91f30601381677.jpg&h=4f0c1819&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2Sp02t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2Sp02t.jpg&h=b0129186&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d63d0820d18b8e3fa42f4bdc34d92645bfe74e72","tid":223160,"uid":77844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:02:41.000Z","msg":"由Zagreb去16湖係咪都係巴士為主？"},{"pid":"fb9cdf662e11e8ebfd9ae1e8ad2c8ce7149adabe","tid":223160,"uid":74458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"去wien或者可以減一日budapest 去下bratislava?"},{"pid":"b182de59f075b4b61e526d378b4e12c22fc714ca","tid":223160,"uid":5402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去wien或者可以減一日budapest 去下bratislava?</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得減一日Budapest 去Bratislava 地方細細 但夠睇哂一日 ！ 有個超大型既mall 雖然無咩好行 不過都幾舒服<br />\n唔知點解咁多人話budapest 好 我覺得Budapest 好舊 d地又爛 而且好多人會埋黎問你買唔買420  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56446a9aa22d1ab3dbd0ceebadf5c2cf743c047","tid":223160,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0